01:12:08,570 --> 01:12:09,280
with that energy?

1578
01:12:09,280 --> 01:12:13,007

1579
01:12:13,007 --> 01:12:14,840
Are there ways in which
it's a bad estimate?

1580
01:12:14,840 --> 01:12:17,798

