01:14:35,176 --> 01:14:38,220

1644
01:14:38,220 --> 01:14:40,490
And let's imagine
something like this.

1645
01:14:40,490 --> 01:14:45,250
And if we chose the
energy just right,

1646
01:14:45,250 --> 01:14:48,120
we would get it to match
to a linear combination

1647
01:14:48,120 --> 01:14:50,560
of collapsing and
growing exponentials,

1648
01:14:50,560 --> 01:14:52,585
where the contribution
from the growing

1649
01:14:52,585 --> 01:14:54,210
exponential in this
direction vanishes.

1650
01:14:54,210 --> 01:14:57,180

1651
01:14:57,180 --> 01:14:59,430
There's precisely one
value of the energy that

1652
01:14:59,430 --> 01:15:01,992
